# 🎬 FrameBeat — AI Music Video Generator
FrameBeat turns your music into a complete music video production package in seconds.
Upload any song and our AI analyzes the audio energy, tempo, and mood — then generates
a full music video concept tailored to your track.
## ✨ Features
- 🎵 Upload local songs (MP3, WAV, OGG, M4A, FLAC)
- ⚡ Real-time audio energy & BPM analysis
- 🎬 Scene-by-scene storyboard with shot types & locations
- ✍️ Auto-generated song lyrics
- 🎨 Color grading & visual style direction
- 🎥 Camera & cinematography recommendations
- 💰 Production budget estimate
- 📄 Export full script
## 🚀 How to Use
1. Open the website
2. Upload your song or drag & drop it
3. Fill in your artist name and video concept
4. Hit **Generate Music Video**
5. Get your full production package instantly
## 🛠️ Built With
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Web Audio API (audio analysis)
- Claude AI (Anthropic)
